@4175 = ~I was waiting for you, nature's friend!~
@4176 = ~I know. Tell me what you must, dear animal!~
@4177 = ~A shadow lord has spread his darkness in the temple ruins near Umar Hills. Did you know that?~
@4178 = ~With all the darkness he has put around, you will have no chance to see what you need to see in that area.~
@4179 = ~Thanks to your efforts, the darkness the Shade Lord had spread around in the temple ruins near Umar Hills is dispelled. Now, you can see what you need to see there.~